		\r\n3	የአንደኛ ሩብ ዓመት ግኝት ፡-\r\n\r\nበኤሌክትሮኒክስ ክፍያ ዘዴ መፈፀም ሲገባዉ በሳጥን /በካዝና/ ብር 50,000.00 የተቆጠረ መገኘቱ፤\r\n		\r\n\r\nያዘጋጀው                                             	             	ማስተካከያ ስለመውስዱ ያረጋገጠው የውስጥ ኦዲተር   \r\nስም _____________________		ፊርማ  ______________		ስም   ___________________   ፊርማ  _____________________\r\n          ያፀደቀዉ ኃላፊ \r\nስም  ____________________     ፊርማ ________________\r\n','Report','approved','Yes','lnstitute of foreignaffairs 2017 1 2 3.pdf','C:/AMSReports/ywolde@mofed.gov.et/lnstitute of foreignaffairs 2017 1 2 3.pdf',NULL,3,'11169',89,'Audit-010',114,89),(789,'derejesrt@gmail.com','2025-05-28 15:27:27.000000','ywolde@mofed.gov.et','2025-05-29 09:13:10.000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Follow up 2nd 2017.pdf','C:/AMSReports/derejesrt@gmail.com/Follow up 2nd 2017.pdf',NULL,NULL,NULL,'','Report','Assigned','default','Follow up 2nd 2017.pdf','C:/AMSReports/ywolde@mofed.gov.et/Follow up 2nd 2017.pdf',NULL,3,'zk-14',NULL,'Audit 2023',192,80),(790,'derejesrt@gmail.com','2025-05-28 15:28:50.000000','ywolde@mofed.gov.et','2025-05-29 09:13:45.000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Amanuel Gebriel and Others.pdf','C:/AMSReports/derejesrt@gmail.com/Amanuel Gebriel and Others.pdf',NULL,NULL,NULL,'','Report','Assigned','default','Amanuel Gebriel and Others.pdf','C:/AMSReports/ywolde@mofed.gov.et/Amanuel Gebriel and Others.pdf',NULL,2,'zk-14',NULL,'Audit 2023',192,80),(791,'mtadele020@gmail.com','2025-05-29 10:48:55.000000','ywolde@mofed.gov.et','2025-08-08 09:58:47.000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'eth natianal library 2017 3.pdf','C:/AMSReports/mtadele020@gmail.com/eth natianal library 2017 3.pdf',NULL,NULL,NULL,'','Report','approved','default','eth natianal library 2017 3.pdf','C:/AMSReports/ywolde@mofed.gov.et/eth natianal library 2017 3.pdf',NULL,3,'nat_l',123,'Audit-010',223,123),(792,'azi.worku@gmail.com','2025-05-29 11:47:15.000000','ateshome@mofed.gov.et','2025-06-20 10:10:25.000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Exicutive summary (2).pdf','C:/AMSReports/azi.worku@gmail.com/Exicutive summary (2).